{"tid":653917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【點都走唔甩】暖心西裝友馬路狂奔追賊 「我係200米跑手 你跑唔贏我㗎」","createTime":"2018-05-05T07:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T07:31:41.000Z","uid":150685,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd00f5b93a11e402a3d623fdac35fb678925b9c","tid":653917,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180505/large/1525467997_25d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525467997_25d9.jpg&h=a74341e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名高中時代的短跑好手，雖已年屆35歲，但寶刀未老，在倫敦街頭發揮其驚人跑速，成功追截一名搶手機的匪徒，網民紛激讚他的英勇行為。<br />\n<br />\n事發當天，任職洋服公司的馬蒂-湯瑪士(Lewychino Martey-Thomas)正值午飯小休，他身穿整齊西裝、打著「煲呔」，正在享受「飯後煙」，突然聽到一名女士高叫「我的手機，我的手機」，周圍一陣哄動。<br />\n<br />\n馬蒂-湯瑪士走近，見到搶匪已被其他人截停，但矢口否認搶手機。馬蒂-湯瑪士挺身而出，向搶匪表示已行使公民逮捕權把他拘捕，命令他把手機交出。在馬蒂-湯瑪士施壓下，搶匪乖乖從褲袋拿出手機，繼而表示想定一定神，要求馬蒂-湯瑪士給他一支香煙。<br />\n<br />\n馬蒂-湯瑪士答應，但警告他「我讀書時是短跑明星，不要嘗試走，我會捉到你」。搶匪可能想試探他是否說真話，竟真的逃跑，馬蒂-湯瑪士立刻展露他的跑速，迅速追及搶匪再把他擒住。他對搶匪說：「我是200米跑手，不要再想走，你跑不贏我，這不會發生。」<br />\n<br />\n目擊事件的人紛紛在網上分享此事，網民都激讚他的義舉，但馬蒂-湯瑪士表示自己不是英雄，只是盡公民責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180505/58150416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58150416&d=ZrrFDRUuioFNkS1lvnVclxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7ebc911f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58150416&h=f61348d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180505/58150416</a>"},{"pid":"d84d80c2ffd904ec4886c3591ac8b617ad2a624c","tid":653917,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"我後生係賽跑冠軍黎架"},{"pid":"5432989f620871598ebcfdae60d9012a3ccc52c1","tid":653917,"uid":40550,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"講得出做得到既人真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a721629aeae2408e2ba9c4610a9e9dd0567b5c","tid":653917,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"真唔真啊"},{"pid":"ce3726c36e89fb078760ce86dd528cf470d7fc3e","tid":653917,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d84d80c2ffd904ec4886c3591ac8b617ad2a624c","tid":653917,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"我後生係賽跑冠軍黎架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"50年前嘛！"},{"pid":"14b39a3b44f9152b5ae0593345b704f1831ef825","tid":653917,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c910e0510ba683d9ffd6c79dcc4382648e69e8b","tid":653917,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻 好man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642cf53207f1cea465aea961c70e1473a8fe2c92","tid":653917,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"條友依家咁有自信 過多二三十年都唔知點算"},{"pid":"bd5688f3b8df080518e5f8c52bf9cd9481e099c4","tid":653917,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"c27efc0d7ecfba8cf9202e52936a842a6943db4f","tid":653917,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affb1435baefaafd7bbd8ce6c92c0c53f0f76c41","tid":653917,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"5b928f0da14f1ab1126fe97b2dcd7e9dc2313d0e","tid":653917,"uid":1